<td style="padding:0 5px;" align="right"><small class="editlink noprint plainlinksneverexpand"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:American_and_British_English_differences&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:American_and_British_English_differences&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">edit box</a></small></td>
