<li id="cite_note-43"><b><a href="#cite_ref-43" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://itre.cis.upenn.edu/~myl/languagelog/archives/000918.html" class="external text" title="http://itre.cis.upenn.edu/~myl/languagelog/archives/000918.html" rel="nofollow">Language Log: More timewasting garbage, another copy-editing moron</a></li>
